texts.text: >The Liberators continue to defeat Chi You's brothers,
>and save human captives in the process.
Eat this!
*Scream*
No, at this rate... Wait, I know!

Hey, humans!
Look over here!
*Whimper*
A hostage?!

*Snicker*
Try attacking now...
Fool.
What?!
Using your power to take a hostage. How can you call yourself my brother?

I, uhh...
T-Thank you very much...
Get back!
*Squeal*
Everything's clear on our end.

One, two... Oh!
I think that's all of them.
That should be everyone that were taken by the demons!
Thank goodness they were all unharmed.

Ain't that the truth.
Aight, what's next...?
Still, you could've been a little nicer back there. She's just a kid.
You ended up saving her,
but what would you've don if you failed?
Nothing different. I still would have felled my opponent.
Children are weak.
Letting your guard down out of pity would have dire consequences.
We're out here to save the people you consider weak.
In terms of failure and success, if that kid dies back there,
then we would've failed in our goal.
How can you say such things...?
I don't care what you think. That's how we're doing things from now on.
Gakuto...
Is this what you truly believe is worth fighting for?
Yeah, I do.
I see...
Then, I shall continue to fight while complying with your demands.
>The fog slowly begins to lift with each demon that is defeated.
The fog's finally starting to dissipate.
That Gate's beginning to shrink too. Does that mean...?
There are far fewer of my brothers here now, and less fog as a result.
Victory is in our grasp.
Yo, that means there ain't that many demons left, right?
We gotta get these folks out of here ASAP.
Meat Balloon, know a good way out that's not crawlin' with demons?
With this crowd? I doubt we'll be able to dodge everything,
but I'll do what I can.
*Roar*
*Scream*
*Strike*
A-Are you okay?
Y-Yeah, but my leg...

You've hurt your leg.
Here, I'll lend you a hand.

Another attack.
Yo, how are y'all doin' back there?
We haven't lost anyone, but a lot are injured!
No deaths means we're doing just fine. We've lucky to not have any on our hands yet.
This fog made it difficult for everyone to react quickly.
It benefitted us when we were attacking Chi You's brothers...
But it's become a liability now that we're on the defensive...
Sorry, I'm trying to find the most demon-free routes I can...
All good, bro. We don't have to fight as much thanks to you.

I remember this part.
The exit has to be close.
Keep going. Don't lose focus.
Yes, ma'am! I swear to complete my mission by getting everybody out of here!
This way... Yes, the exit should be just up ahead!

Really?!
I can go home!
I can see mom!
Hey, hold up...!
>Gakuto stops everyone right in front of the exit,
>which is blocked by an army of demons.
I have been waiting for you, humans.
How dare you ruin our contest...!
An ambush?! Here?!
I know that you are the ones protecting those other humans.
Did you plan on leaving while my eyes were looking elsewhere?
They saw right through our plan.
What do we do, Megakin?
Yo, what choice do we have? We ain't got anywhere else to go.
We gotta lead the way and fight our way out!
Then, we can get everyone out of this place!
Copy that!
You will regret dabbling in our affairs!

Let's go!
Devil Download!
>The Liberators lead a charge towards the demons with everyone else in tow.
>However...
A frontal assault' isn't gonna work...!
We can't fight while protecting everyone else at the same time!
You thinking about ditching them?
Hey, don't say stuff like that! I don't care if you're jokin'!
We're gonna protect everyone and get them outta here!
(Ignoring the weaklings and aiming directly for the commander would be most prudent.)
(Pyrrhic victory or not, a win is still a win.)
(Why do they not do that? I simply do not understand...)
Brotheeerrr!!!
>Chi You falls to his knees as his brother's spear makes contact.
*Wince*
You have become so weak.
To think that such a simple attack would bring the eldest to his knees!
Indeed, peace is meaningless! Even you have fallen victim to it, brother!
I will change this world! Right after I deal with you!!
N-Nooo...!
>Chi You's brothers unleash a series of vicious attacks on him.
(No, if only I did not waste so much energy protecting those pathetic humans...!)
(Or have I actually become as weak as they say...?)
(Has the conviction of these humans caused by skills to dull?)
(Regardless, the battle has been decided. Such a bleak situation...)
(Huang Di was cornered like this countless times...)
(Yet he never gave up. He always found a way to turn a battle on its head.)

(How did he do that?
How...?)
(No, I will not find the answer like this...)

*Roar*
Die!
>Chi You closes his eyes and accepts defeat at the hands of his brother.
>But he does not feel his brother's spear piercing him.
What is the matter, brother? You have won. Finish it...
>Chi You opens his eyes and sees...
*Wince*
>The girl from before struggling against the demon.
